headline: LPL Financial Holdings Inc. (LPLA) Surpasses Q3 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: LPL Financial (LPLA) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +16.33% and +3.65%, respectively, for the quarter ended September 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?
